# Staging Rollout

This rollout uses the reusable workflow at `.github/workflows/reusable_release.yml`.

Dispatch the top-level release workflow with `manifest_path: release/manifest.v2.toml` and `target_environment: staging`.

The reusable workflow publishes the `artifact_manifest` output as `artifacts/release-manifest.json`.

Run staging smoke with `python deploy/check_release.py --env staging --emit-json artifacts/release_smoke_report.json`.

